the last five years

00:36:01.340 --> 00:36:03.800
that we've seen
the tipping point.

00:36:03.800 --> 00:36:05.740
But we still have to look at--

00:36:05.740 --> 00:36:07.610
we're at a point
now if they just

00:36:07.610 --> 00:36:12.370
stripped subsidies of all kinds
off of every source of energy,

00:36:12.370 --> 00:36:15.570
the renewables would
just take over.

00:36:15.570 --> 00:36:18.600
So this idea of
saying we're not going

00:36:18.600 --> 00:36:20.310
